{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_MntrFloorFire}}
'''A_MntrFloorFire'''<br />
(no parameters)

Spawns a {{Class|MinotaurFX3}} near the calling actor's position, randomly within four map units on both X and Y axes. The spawned flames are given the calling actor's target, so this codepointer should be called only by missiles, not directly by a monster. It is restricted to {{Class|MinotaurFX2}} and derived classes.

